Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.80,0:02:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第五十八話\N時代選擇志志雄？\N劍心最大的危機!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.97,0:03:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正世間是弱肉強食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.71,0:03:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那句話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.48,0:03:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我教導宗次郎的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.45,0:03:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這句話不光是指劍術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.32,0:03:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以一句話來說   大自然的法則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.19,0:03:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弱者身為強者的糧食\N有活下去的責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.73,0:03:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連糧食都當不了的東西\N其存在是半點價值也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.03,0:03:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最強的強者站在最頂端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.77,0:03:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比我弱小的明治政府那些人\N沒資格掌握這個國家的霸權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.81,0:03:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夠資格掌握霸權的人  只有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.55,0:03:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奪得這個國家\N就是這國家的法則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.55,0:03:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強者生 弱者死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.69,0:03:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是經歷幕末時代\N腥風血雨的殺人狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.06,0:04:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該瞭解違反這個法則\N是徒勞無功的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.93,0:04:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不瞭解…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.26,0:04:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你口中的糧食 那些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.83,0:04:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是熬過那動亂的時代\N好不容易得到和平世界的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.97,0:04:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了誰 或為某種東西\N而理當犧牲的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.64,0:04:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不存在這個世間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.98,0:04:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你堅持再度掀起動亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.32,0:04:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管你有什麼理由\N我都不能置之不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.02,0:04:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過不是理由 是法則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.69,0:04:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是法則 我也辦不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.36,0:04:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是那樣子\N不論情況怎樣都不屈服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.33,0:04:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任何人都絕對無法\N動搖這傢伙的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.37,0:04:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是照這樣下去\N他的身體一定會先崩潰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.68,0:05:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來就算你的腦袋理解\N你的情緒還是無法理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.15,0:05:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從你冥頑不靈\N堅持不殺原則這一點來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.72,0:05:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你本來就是這種人\N你的腦袋那麼差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.49,0:05:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斬人拔刀齊的名聲\N真的是一敗塗地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.50,0:05:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與其活著丟臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.67,0:05:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得你還不知\N在這裏壯烈成仁來得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.04,0:05:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣我至少會在我創造的\N新歷史中留下你的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.55,0:05:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論是你創造的歷史\N還是今後的歷史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.92,0:05:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都不打算留下我的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.85,0:05:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.49,0:05:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有一樣東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.39,0:05:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在動亂之後來到的\N和平的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.53,0:05:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.37,0:05:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笑死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.00,0:05:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平的世界？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.17,0:05:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在西洋諸國以武力欺壓人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.87,0:06:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在世界各地爭奪殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.58,0:06:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰知道日本何時會\N落入列國的統治下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.08,0:06:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時候這個國家\N什麼對應措施也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.42,0:06:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至今薩摩、長州\N政爭還是鬧個不斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.36,0:06:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你所說的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.49,0:06:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是擺著好看的空想罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.73,0:06:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以藉由動亂而非空想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.80,0:06:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來讓這國家的笨蛋們\N認識到弱肉強食的現實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.14,0:06:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在做的事\N是要讓這個國家覺醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.48,0:06:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然劍心的氣勢\N被志志雄壓倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.95,0:06:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不得不使出絕技\N天翔龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.59,0:06:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與蒼紫和宗次郎\N接連兩次的交手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.49,0:06:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使他消耗的體力超出預料了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.28,0:07:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強者生 弱者死嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.38,0:07:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你所說的法則\N把那個青年害得有多慘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.82,0:07:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你所想像不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.76,0:07:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強者生 弱者死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.73,0:07:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.36,0:07:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到頭來這世間弱者\N還是死路一條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.73,0:07:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有強者才能活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.94,0:07:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是現實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.94,0:07:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我無法理解   我無法理解緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.61,0:07:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的一切…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.54,0:07:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候保護我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.41,0:07:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是志志雄教導我的真理\N以及一把短刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.15,0:07:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以正確的是志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.82,0:07:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 身為弱者\N真的那麼不該嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.03,0:08:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是殺人了\N可是其實我並不想殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.06,0:08:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想殺人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.83,0:08:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道對你而言\N連宗次郎都只是糧食嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.71,0:08:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 輸給你\N表示他也是弱者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.68,0:08:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以他遵從法則\N很勇敢的成為我的糧食了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.25,0:08:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消耗你的體力\N把天翔龍閃的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.89,0:08:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當成向我告別的贈禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.99,0:08:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告別的贈禮…是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.10,0:08:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣我就放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.57,0:08:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你口中的弱者\N糧食的那位青年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.80,0:08:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將經由與你訣別這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.24,0:08:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再也不受縛於勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.41,0:08:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將來有天他一定會\N從自己的生活方式中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.38,0:08:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出真實的答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.72,0:08:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這男人太不聰明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.39,0:09:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管怎麼掙扎 你與宗次郎\N都逃不過自然的法則的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.56,0:09:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說誰在逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.80,0:09:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得我給你忠告你不聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.13,0:09:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.37,0:09:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會讓你痛快死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.64,0:09:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在倒下去還太早了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.92,0:09:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個手背套 這個味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.72,0:09:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過你還是壯烈成仁最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.79,0:09:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是火藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.42,0:09:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.06,0:09:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,貳之秘劍 紅蓮腕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.15,0:10:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.59,0:10:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是真的吧 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.33,0:10:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼 真的死了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.90,0:10:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還沒使出天翔龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.51,0:10:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不夠看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.98,0:10:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,9分又53秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.15,0:10:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害我擔心一場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.48,0:10:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我見識到紅蓮腕的威力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.82,0:10:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用焰靈讓手背套的火藥爆炸\N太厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.66,0:10:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是志志雄大人\N做事毫無破綻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.19,0:10:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死人了 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.03,0:10:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別嘍嗦了 快善後吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.10,0:10:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.67,0:10:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才收拾掉一個受傷的人\N就放鬆戒心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.77,0:10:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論過去或現在\N都是你的致命傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.88,0:11:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄真實   你的真實我要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.43,0:11:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.80,0:11:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.25,0:11:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.78,0:11:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才確實有砍中啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.77,0:11:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如同有次我說過的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.64,0:12:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你比誰都靠近我們\N我就猜你一定會來偷襲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.88,0:12:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,缽金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.08,0:12:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那次被放火燒的時候\N我由於腦部受到重擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.82,0:12:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法行動 才吃了大虧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.16,0:12:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以為了避免重蹈覆轍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.73,0:12:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有這裏 我做了重點補強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.46,0:12:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你調查得不夠徹底哦   齊藤一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.07,0:12:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你讓\N千載難逢的勝利機會逃過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.07,0:12:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的腳傷 是宇水給你的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.91,0:12:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來那也幫上一點忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.65,0:12:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以你受傷的腳\N還能做這種長距離的牙突
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.12,0:12:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實了得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.09,0:12:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.29,0:12:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才是最後一次   你沒機會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.26,0:13:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就到黃泉與拔刀齊敘舊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.66,0:13:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們會談得很愉快的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.70,0:13:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在還不能死   除非你先死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.74,0:13:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到前新撰組的齊藤一\N會為無用的明治政府賣命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.62,0:13:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底是為何而戰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.62,0:13:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會是像拔刀齊一樣\N為了天真的正義吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.33,0:13:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我戰鬥的目的\N不論過去現在都只有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.80,0:13:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是為自己的正義而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.40,0:13:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是 惡即斬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.51,0:13:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒道理的惡即斬嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.21,0:13:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟拔刀齊不同 易懂多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.72,0:14:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接招吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.80,0:14:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個招術被我看過\N第二次就行不通了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.21,0:14:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雙腿的傷\N好像讓你行動遲緩很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.75,0:14:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是\N宇水確實成為我的糧食了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.72,0:14:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然 那點程度的刺擊\N就算你沒受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.99,0:14:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我依然是不放在眼裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.91,0:14:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說得對\N現在的齊藤是沒有勝算的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.68,0:15:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…但是現在除了牙突\N也無法依賴別的了 齊藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.39,0:15:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此 這就是你的…\N不 是新撰組的戰鬥方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.70,0:15:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我見識\N壬生狼活躍的樣子吧 來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.50,0:15:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牙突二式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.65,0:15:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牙突三式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.34,0:15:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還真是死心眼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.17,0:15:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我看你絕招似乎用完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.44,0:16:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過 你太大意了\N傻瓜病是不會好死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.75,0:16:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牙突零式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.03,0:16:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大意？你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.90,0:16:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這叫做從容 知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.77,0:16:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在零距離射程內使出牙突\N你這政府的走狗還挺能幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.51,0:16:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你跟拔刀齊不同\N是真的想殺我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.22,0:16:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我會在我的時代\N留下你的名字的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.81,0:17:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.66,0:17:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還在啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.43,0:17:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要逃的話就快趁現在\N如果愛惜性命的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.06,0:17:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一點也不怕死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.33,0:17:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算死 我也不會一個人死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.74,0:17:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會把你拉下地獄同行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.64,0:17:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夜還沒深呢 你別講夢話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.11,0:17:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才你應該看到了\N眼前發生的現實才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.05,0:17:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳說中的斬人拔刀齊緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.62,0:17:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及前新撰組三號隊長 齊藤一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.86,0:18:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一下子就在我面前落敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.30,0:18:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是自然的法則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.47,0:18:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弱肉強食是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.77,0:18:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.87,0:18:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿弱者當食物吃\N由最強的你站在最上面嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.91,0:18:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.98,0:18:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.05,0:18:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心不是為了那樣的世界\N而戰鬥到現在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.79,0:18:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 維新還沒有結束呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.16,0:18:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 形式上的維新在十年前成立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.33,0:18:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為新時代明治了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.80,0:18:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是真正需要幸福的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.97,0:18:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們還處於\N弱者受欺凌的舊時代中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.64,0:18:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我想盡微薄之力\N幫助那些人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.58,0:18:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而揮舞這把劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.68,0:18:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心不像你以弱者為糧食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.79,0:19:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他還自願成為弱者的糧食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.72,0:19:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個結果就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.16,0:19:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒你出場的份\N戰鬥已經結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.50,0:19:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.05,0:19:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.09,0:19:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,方治 我替你折斷他五六根肋骨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.76,0:19:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的要煎要煮\N就隨便你玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.43,0:19:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.50,0:19:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒完…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.47,0:19:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐 小惠 大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.31,0:19:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 我沒保護好劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.55,0:20:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是就算要付出這條命\N我也一定要讓事情有個了結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.69,0:20:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二重極
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.96,0:20:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要攻過來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.56,0:20:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就該先填捕這…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.07,0:20:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巨大的實力差之後…再攻過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.64,0:21:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太強了 太強了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.98,0:21:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我方治確實沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.85,0:21:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有志志雄大人在\N奪取國家政權就很有可能了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.66,0:21:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快殺死他 志志雄大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.92,0:21:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些傢伙的韌性不比普通人\N趁現在快殺死他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.36,0:21:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別那麼急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.03,0:21:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很久沒這樣主動出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.63,0:22:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再讓我多沉浸在\N勝利的餘韻中一會兒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.80,0:22:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 要下殺手或品味勝利的餘韻都還太早了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.69,0:22:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四乃森蒼紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.76,0:22:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都忘記了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.89,0:22:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實還有一個手下敗將\N留著沒處理呢

